    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/f994ce4fe3a0663f9204b1c1ac0d8341.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/f994ce4fe3a0663f9204b1c1ac0d8341.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏预计在2025年发售！官方QQ群：469744523</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/5b2e6f99d4d9bd427d4d461d2e224ab8.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/5b2e6f99d4d9bd427d4d461d2e224ab8.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏是校园+日常+双线+奇幻超能力的视觉小说故事，游戏将以“依露琳”作为游玩主角并通过它的视角来了解这一故事背后的真相，“时光回溯”交换的代价究竟是？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/21f2b2d67281feed1461aad0fc6a276d.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/21f2b2d67281feed1461aad0fc6a276d.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=4008 /></span><strong> </strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/0fbab897d5a48b824c4d81ee37e50d2a.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/0fbab897d5a48b824c4d81ee37e50d2a.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=3388 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/16ffb1bca6271a552eb7f7485aad7b0c.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/16ffb1bca6271a552eb7f7485aad7b0c.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=3534 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/8ea6ed17a7d929debc02fe39da4ee08c.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/8ea6ed17a7d929debc02fe39da4ee08c.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=1920 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/9c7fd6064242a45b45b7312bbf5b1560.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/9c7fd6064242a45b45b7312bbf5b1560.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=2600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏简介</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras/75b77ee85f584ac8313b1413be2fff1c.avif?t=1760351758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399700/extras_big/75b77ee85f584ac8313b1413be2fff1c.avif?t=1760351758 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「荷莱」（Horae）是一款由北京黎羽科技制作并发行的买断制视觉小说游戏，游戏将围绕少女的爱慕之情，描绘原本普通的青春校园恋爱故事，直到这名少女意外发现了自己拥有回到过去12小时以前的能力，在谋求幸福的道路上，另一位少女爱上了她，并以她为核心展开了奇妙的多角恋爱关系，故事也由此展开，目前游戏正在开发中，未来在2025年会登陆Steam平台发布。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成绩不好还调皮的依露林暗恋着优等生梵逸，而梵逸和隔壁班的优等生黎羽相互产生好感，原本只是发生在普通县城普通中学的普通和青春相关的普通三角恋爱故事，却因为依露林所获得的时间回溯的能力而发生了改变 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她大摇大摆的迟到并且和号称校内最严厉有着‘教头’一称的教导主任针尖对麦芒，明明完全没有复习却能够考出极为优秀的成绩，在无聊的课程中一跃而起，改变了老师们的上课节奏，把别人一辈子想要在课堂上做的事情在短时间内做了个遍 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她依靠这份能力和梵逸站在了学校的同一个高度，但也因为这份能力而使得周围人们的生活出现了极大的变故，但随着时间的流逝，依露林才发现了使用这份能力的代价，并企图回到原来的世界去</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
